## Project Structure
-   `/app`: Main source code.
-   `/app/src/app`: Page routes (Next.js App Router).
-   `/app/src/components`: Reusable UI components.
-   `/app/src/lib`: Mock data and utilities.

## Local Development
1.  `npm install`
2.  `npm run dev`

